<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 07 Jan 2025 12:29:15 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>西藏地震多发区发生震颤</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/tremors-earthquake-prone-tibet-2025-01-07/</link><description>周二，西藏发生里氏 6.8 级地震，这是近年来最强烈的地震之一，袭击了喜马拉雅山北麓，造成至少 95 人死亡。</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 Jan 2025 12:14:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/tremors-earthquake-prone-tibet-2025-01-07/</guid></item><item><title>中国称美国对中国无人机存在安全风险的怀疑是“不负责任的”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-says-us-suspicion-security-risks-chinese-drones-is-irresponsible-2025-01-07/</link><description>中国商务部周二表示，中国称美国“毫无根据地怀疑”中国无人机系统存在信息安全风险，“极其不负责任”。</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 Jan 2025 11:27:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-says-us-suspicion-security-risks-chinese-drones-is-irresponsible-2025-01-07/</guid></item><item><title>早间出价：市场现实的震撼</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2025-01-07/</link><description>阿曼达·库珀 (Amanda Cooper) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望。</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 Jan 2025 11:04:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2025-01-07/</guid></item><item><title>中国奇瑞报告2024年销量增长38.4%至260万辆</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-chery-reports-384-jump-2024-sales-26-mln-vehicles-2025-01-07/</link><description>中国汽车制造商奇瑞 (CHERY.UL) 周二报告称，2024 年全球汽车销量将增长 38.4%，达到 260 万辆，并预计今年销量将超过 300 万辆。</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 Jan 2025 10:39:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-chery-reports-384-jump-2024-sales-26-mln-vehicles-2025-01-07/</guid></item><item><title>韩国被弹劾的领导人尹正蹲在首尔的“比佛利山庄”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/south-koreas-impeached-leader-yoon-hunkers-down-seouls-beverly-hills-2025-01-07/</link><description>周二，在调查人员计划逮捕他的同时，被弹劾的韩国总统尹锡烈和他的妻子、狗和猫仍然躲在一排排铁丝网和一小队个人保安后面，躲在他那座庞大的山坡别墅里。</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 Jan 2025 10:18:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/south-koreas-impeached-leader-yoon-hunkers-down-seouls-beverly-hills-2025-01-07/</guid></item><item><title>特朗普获胜引发海外投资者2024年退出亚洲股市</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/trump-win-triggered-2024-exit-by-overseas-investors-asian-equities-2025-01-07/</link><description>海外投资者在 2024 年转向亚洲股票的净卖家，主要是由于担心美国当选总统唐纳德·特朗普的贸易政策可能打击亚洲经济体，上季度抛售激增。</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 Jan 2025 09:31:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/trump-win-triggered-2024-exit-by-overseas-investors-asian-equities-2025-01-07/</guid></item><item><title>贸易商称，中国山东港口集团禁止美国制裁的油轮</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/chinas-shandong-port-group-blacklists-us-sanctioned-oil-vessels-say-traders-2025-01-07/</link><description>三名贸易商称，中国山东港口集团周一发布通知，禁止美国制裁的油船停靠中国东海岸的港口。</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 Jan 2025 09:07:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/chinas-shandong-port-group-blacklists-us-sanctioned-oil-vessels-say-traders-2025-01-07/</guid></item><item><title>泰国官员称在缅甸失踪的中国演员可能是人口贩运受害者</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinese-actor-missing-near-thai-myanmar-border-found-thai-officials-say-2025-01-07/</link><description>泰国当局周二表示，上周在泰缅边境附近失踪的一名中国演员已在缅甸找到，他可能是人口贩卖的受害者。</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 Jan 2025 09:00:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinese-actor-missing-near-thai-myanmar-border-found-thai-officials-say-2025-01-07/</guid></item><item><title>前律师称中国新冠抗议电影制片人被判入狱</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-covid-protest-filmmaker-sentenced-prison-former-lawyer-says-2025-01-07/</link><description>一名中国导演的前律师表示，一名拍摄了一部关于 2022 年“白皮书”示威活动、反对中国新冠疫情限制措施的中国导演，本周被上海一家法院判处三年半有期徒刑。</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 Jan 2025 08:45:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-covid-protest-filmmaker-sentenced-prison-former-lawyer-says-2025-01-07/</guid></item><item><title>中国对印度氯氰菊酯征收反倾销保证金</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-impose-anti-dumping-deposits-cypermethrin-india-2025-01-07/</link><description>中国商务部周二表示，经初步调查发现，自1月8日起，将对原产于印度的氯氰菊酯征收反倾销保证金。</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 Jan 2025 08:12:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-impose-anti-dumping-deposits-cypermethrin-india-2025-01-07/</guid></item><item><title>沃尔沃汽车 12 月销量下降 3%，电动汽车销量增长</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/volvo-cars-december-sales-down-3-2025-01-07/</link><description>总部位于瑞典的汽车制造商沃尔沃汽车周二表示，由于混合动力汽车销量下降，沃尔沃汽车 12 月份销量同比下降 3%，至 73,804 辆。</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 Jan 2025 08:05:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/volvo-cars-december-sales-down-3-2025-01-07/</guid></item><item><title>新加坡考虑立法保护宗族、商业协会免受外国干涉</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/singapore-considers-law-guard-clans-business-associations-against-foreign-2025-01-07/</link><description>新加坡周二出台立法，保护与种族群体有联系的宗族和商业协会免受外国干涉。</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 Jan 2025 08:02:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/singapore-considers-law-guard-clans-business-associations-against-foreign-2025-01-07/</guid></item><item><title>中国出口推动新日铁在交易受阻后寻求在美国和印度寻求增长</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/china-exports-push-nippon-steel-seek-growth-us-india-after-blocked-deal-2025-01-07/</link><description>分析人士称，在白宫阻止其收购美国钢铁公司后，新日铁准备扩大其在美国和印度的业务，以寻求增长并免受中国廉价出口产品的影响。</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 Jan 2025 07:59:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/china-exports-push-nippon-steel-seek-growth-us-india-after-blocked-deal-2025-01-07/</guid></item><item><title>中方重视特朗普同习近平会谈的表态</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china-attaches-importance-trumps-remarks-talks-with-xi-2025-01-07/</link><description>中国外交部在回应美国当选总统特朗普周一的言论时表示，中国“高度重视”特朗普的言论，称他一直在通过助手与中国国家主席习近平进行会谈。</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 Jan 2025 07:48:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china-attaches-importance-trumps-remarks-talks-with-xi-2025-01-07/</guid></item><item><title>2024年中国住宅止赎数量因房地产市场低迷而增加</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-residential-foreclosures-increase-2024-amid-property-slump-2025-01-07/</link><description>周二的一项私营部门调查显示，2024 年中国止赎房屋的数量较上一年有所增加，加剧了人们对房地产低迷和经济增长不平衡的情况下抵押贷款拖欠的担忧。</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 Jan 2025 07:05:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-residential-foreclosures-increase-2024-amid-property-slump-2025-01-07/</guid></item></channel></rss>